cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Auto Dataset Builder in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Auto Dataset Builder: An LLM-Assisted Framework for Automatic Dataset Construction"
abstract: >
  Auto Dataset Builder (ADB) is an end-to-end platform that transforms natural language
  descriptions into annotated, training-ready computer vision datasets. It integrates
  a three-stage annotation pipeline (YOLOv11, SAM2, Vision LLM) with a novel Neural
  Dataset Quality Score (Neural DQS) that predicts model mAP from five interpretable
  dataset-level features.
